@ScheduleApiHost = http://127.0.0.1:5080
@ExternalApiKey = compass-local-external-api-key
@ProjectId = site-renewal

### 接続クライアントと利用可能なスコープ
GET {{ScheduleApiHost}}/api/external/v1/
Accept: application/json
X-Compass-Api-Key: {{ExternalApiKey}}

### 軽量な案件一覧
GET {{ScheduleApiHost}}/api/external/v1/projects?limit=20
Accept: application/json
X-Compass-Api-Key: {{ExternalApiKey}}

### 案件のタスク計画。レスポンスのETagを更新系APIのIf-Matchへ渡します
GET {{ScheduleApiHost}}/api/external/v1/projects/{{ProjectId}}/tasks
Accept: application/json
X-Compass-Api-Key: {{ExternalApiKey}}

### API定義（開発環境のみ）
GET {{ScheduleApiHost}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json
